        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Semiprecious gemstones emerge, seemingly at random, from the surface of this gnarled wooden staff. While wielding it, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to identify divination magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Detect Magic]{Detect Magic}</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.True Strike]{True Strike}</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Comprehend Language]{Comprehend Language}</em>, <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Darkvision]{Darkvision}</em>, <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.See Invisibility]{See Invisibility}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
